#.rst:
# MToolsConfig
# ------------
#
# CMake :command:`find_package` module for MTools.
#
# IMPORTED Targets
# ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
#
# This package defines the following :prop_tgt:`IMPORTED` targets:
#
# ``Mutant::MHandle``
#   :prop_tgt:`IMPORTED` executable target for using ``mhandle``.
#
# Commands
# ^^^^^^^^
#
# This package defines the following CMake commands (as functions):
#
# .. command:: mutant_add_handles
#
#  Scans source files for any uses of ``MHANDLE``. ::
#
#    MUTANT_ADD_HANDLES(<OUTPUT_FILES> [<SOURCES>...])
#
#  ``OUTPUT_FILES``
#    Variable to define with autogenerated source files.
#  ``SOURCES``
#    C/C++ source files to scan for ``MHANDLE_*``.

